<title>
Auto Steering Lock Inspection (Keyless Push Start Model)
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove steering column lower cover. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B6206003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove steering column hole cover. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B9306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Measure voltage between each terminal of auto steering lock and body ground.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If check result is not as specified, replace auto steering lock (1). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B6206014"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
